Functions for analyzing certificate files.

The main function reads a self-signed certificate and verifies the signature.

To build and run:

	cd src
	make
	./ctool cert.pem

Supported public key algorithms:

	RSA
	prime256v1 (NIST P-256)
	secp384r1 (NIST P-384)

Supported hash algorithms

	MD5
	SHA1
	SHA224
	SHA256
	SHA384
	SHA512
